### download the insight agent ###
login to insight platform https://insight.rapid7.com
and loging with platform account

navigate to data collection management>asset management>add new>agent and select windows/linux agent

then install the agent with given instruction.

@@# for linux agent #@@
systemctl status ir_agent  or service ir_agent status    ### To see the status of insight agent in linux machine
systemctl stop ir_agent      ### To stop the insight agent in Linux machine
systemctl start ir_agent     ### To start the insight agent in linux machine

sudo cat /opt/rapid7/ir_agent/components/insight_agent/common/agent.log | grep "Agent Info" | tail -1l  ### to see the version of linux agent

### Reinstall the agent###
.<installer_extraction_dir>/agent_installer.sh reinstall

.<installer_extraction_dir>/agent_installer.sh reinstall_start

### Uninstall the Agent ###
.<installer_extraction_dir>/agent_installer.sh uninstall



@@# For Windows Agent #@@
open command terminal in windows
sc start ir_agent   ### to start agent in windows
sc stop ir_agent    ### to stop agent in windows

you can also check the status of agent with services.msc

C:\Program Files\Rapid7\Insight Agent\ir_agent.exe -v     ### To check the Version of agent in Windows 


